OL,3,CUnion warns of unfair dismissal claim
OL,4,Cif bin workers are made redundant
OL,6,FBin workers could make unfair
OL,7,Fdismissal claims against Birmingham
OL,8,FCity Council if they are made
OL,9,Fredundant, Unite the Union has warned.
OL,11,FOn Wednesday, the council said all its
OL,12,Foffers had been rejected by the union
OL,13,Fwhich sparked fears of redundancies.
OL,15,FIn response, Unite leader Onay Kasab
OL,16,Ftold ITV News Central: "The council
OL,17,Fhaven't made loads of offers, that's
OL,18,Fabsolute nonsense, they're just trying
OL,19,Fto build a narrative. We've got a
OL,20,Fcouncil who are moving to fire and
OL,21,Frehire.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
