OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F377A1752226211
OL,3,CUnion warns of unfair dismissal claim
OL,4,Cif bin workers are made redundant
OL,6,F"The council leader has been promising
OL,7,Fthat nobody needs to lose any pay -
OL,8,Fthere's not been a single offer from
OL,9,Fthe council that comes anywhere near
OL,10,Fto that."
OL,12,FMr Kasab has now warned that the
OL,13,Fcouncil could face unfair dismissal
OL,14,Fclaims, adding: "There are ways and
OL,15,Fmeans in which employers can implement
OL,16,Ffire and rehire but it doesn't mean
OL,17,Fthat they're safe from unfair
OL,18,Fdismissal claims. That is a real
OL,19,Fpossibility here as well and something
OL,20,Fthat we will be looking into.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
