OL,3,CUnion warns of unfair dismissal claim
OL,4,Cif bin workers are made redundant
OL,6,F"We're talking about pay cuts of
OL,7,Faround #8,000 a year. Our members have
OL,8,Fgot mortgages, rents to pay, food to
OL,9,Fbuy and we shouldn't lose track of
OL,10,Fthat.
OL,12,F"We're not talking about asking for
OL,13,Fmore money, we are talking about
OL,14,Fprotecting the pay of essential public
OL,15,Fservice workers.
OL,17,F"We're still in a position where the
OL,18,Fcouncil are trying to force through
OL,19,Fpay cuts and we're still in a position
OL,20,Fwhere our members are determined to
OL,21,Fresist that by taking strike action."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
