OL,3,CUnion warns of unfair dismissal claim
OL,4,Cif bin workers are made redundant
OL,6,FThe council and the union have been
OL,7,Flocked in a dispute throughout 2025.
OL,9,FIn March, bin workers began their all-
OL,10,Fout strike, leading to rubbish piling
OL,11,Fup on the streets, and recycling
OL,12,Fcollections completely suspended.
OL,14,FCouncil leader John Cotton said in a
OL,15,Fstatement on Wednesday, 9 July:
OL,16,F"Throughout this process, the council
OL,17,Fhas sought to be reasonable and
OL,18,Fflexible, but we have reached the
OL,19,Fabsolute limit of what we can offer.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
