OL,3,CUnion warns of unfair dismissal claim
OL,4,Cif bin workers are made redundant
OL,6,FMr Cotton added: "Unite's demands
OL,7,Fwould leave us with another equal pay
OL,8,Fbill of hundreds of millions of
OL,9,Fpounds, which is totally unacceptable,
OL,10,Fand would jeopardise the considerable
OL,11,Fprogress we have made in our financial
OL,12,Frecovery.
OL,14,F"We must be fair to all our staff, and
OL,15,FI will not repeat the mistakes of the
OL,16,Fpast by making decisions that would
OL,17,Fultimately result in further cuts to
OL,18,Fservices and the sale of more council
OL,19,Fassets.
OL,26,@nD@ROUvD@AOU
