OL,3,CUnion warns of unfair dismissal claim
OL,4,Cif bin workers are made redundant
OL,6,F"Successive administrations have
OL,7,Ffailed to close off the council's
OL,8,Fequal pay liabilities, costing the
OL,9,Fpeople of Birmingham hundreds of
OL,10,Fmillions of pounds and that must end
OL,11,Fnow.
OL,13,F"We need to deliver a better waste
OL,14,Fservice; creating an efficient,
OL,15,Fimproved service is a crucial part of
OL,16,Four need to become financially
OL,17,Fsustainable and is what the people of
OL,18,FBirmingham need. We cannot delay this
OL,19,Fany longer.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
